UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat22;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
bool u_xlatb33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_4.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat33) * u_xlat33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_4.w * u_xlat16_4.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_36 = max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat33;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat16_36 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat33 = min(u_xlat33, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_34;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_36) + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat13.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = log2(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat38 = exp2(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_36) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_14.xxx) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat38 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat38) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat13.x = exp2(u_xlat13.x);
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_40 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_9.x / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat5.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = inversesqrt(u_xlat22);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat22) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = inversesqrt(u_xlat22);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat22) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MatColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.y + -1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = _MatMask * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(u_xlat16_1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat33 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat33) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat16_33 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_33 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat33 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat33) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_ATVECTOR_X" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
Local Keywords { "_RMAP_MATCAP" }
"// hash: e5eecb6b11e5d6c7
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightLerp;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;

precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_0;

bool u_xlatb33;

mediump float u_xlat16_40;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat10_0.x + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb33 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb33){discard;}
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_4.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat33) * u_xlat33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat10_4.w * u_xlat10_4.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_36 = max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat33;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat16_36 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat33 = min(u_xlat33, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_36) + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat13.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat10_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat38 = log2(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat38 = exp2(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat38);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_36) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat38 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-u_xlat16_14.xxx) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat10_3 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat10_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) + (-u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat38 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat38) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat13.x = exp2(u_xlat13.x);
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_40 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_9.x / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat5.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = inversesqrt(u_xlat22);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat22) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat22 = inversesqrt(u_xlat22);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat22) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_5.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_6.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat10_5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MatColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_0.y + -1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = _MatMask * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(u_xlat16_1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat33 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat33) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_33 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat10_33 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat33 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat33) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	float _DigiDistore;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _HairMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _BumpMapNr2_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _colorSkin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowPow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainPlayerPositionWS;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;

uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb30){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = max(u_xlat30, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = abs(u_xlat16_35) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_1.w * u_xlat16_1.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_15) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_15;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat32 = exp2(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat3.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat3.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.y + -1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = _MatMask * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_35 * _RampMap_ST.x + _RampMap_ST.z;
    u_xlat20 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat20 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat20 = exp2(u_xlat20);
    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat20) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat20) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MatColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat30 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat30) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat16_30 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_30 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat30;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat30) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_ADDITIONAL_LIGHTS" "_ATVECTOR_Y" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }

"// hash: bd377dc7ad5a5d4c
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightLerp;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH

precision highp int;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat10_0.x + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb30){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = max(u_xlat30, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = abs(u_xlat16_35) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat10_1.w * u_xlat10_1.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);

    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;

    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat3.x;

    u_xlat20 = u_xlat20 * _DigiPow;

    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat20) + 2.0;

    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat30) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;

}

    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat32;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb30){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = max(u_xlat30, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-u_xlat16_5.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = abs(u_xlat16_35) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_1.w * u_xlat16_1.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_15) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_15;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_16 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat32 = exp2(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat32 = min(max(u_xlat32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat3.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat3.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_0.y + -1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = _MatMask * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_35 * _RampMap_ST.x + _RampMap_ST.z;
    u_xlat20 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat20 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat20 = exp2(u_xlat20);
    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat20) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat20) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MatColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat30 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat30) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat16_30 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_30 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat30;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat30) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

SubProgram "gles " {

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

vec4 u_xlat0;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;

float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;

    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34;

    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_15;

    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat10_1.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;

    u_xlat32 = exp2(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat32 = clamp(u_xlat32, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat3.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat3.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_14 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_0.z * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_0.y + -1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.x;
    u_xlat16_34 = _MatMask * u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_35 * _RampMap_ST.x + _RampMap_ST.z;
    u_xlat20 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat20 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat20 = exp2(u_xlat20);
    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat20) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat20) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MatColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_14 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat30 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat30) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_30 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat10_30 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat30) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat6.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}
